metadata.name: The Sun Will Rise
metadata.description:
I fundamentally believe that as artists it is not only our duty to bring beauty into this world, but also our moral obligation and primary objective to repair and restore the beauty in the lives of the communities we are blessed to be a part of. This NFT photograph is minted on the 27th February 2022, in support of the Ukrainian people's struggle. 100% of the proceeds from the primary sale of these editions will go towards relief efforts in Ukraine. All royalties from secondary sales will either go towards those same efforts or towards other causes that the For Good Fund is actively supporting at the time.

Photograph by [sukrits_25](https://opensea.io/sukrits_25)
